text.section:
In any application for a certificate of title, a person may not:
Fraudulently use a false or fictitious name;
Knowingly make a false statement;
Knowingly conceal a material fact; or
Otherwise commit a fraud in making the application.

In any application for the registration of a vehicle, a person may not:
Fraudulently use a false or fictitious name;
Knowingly make a false statement;
Knowingly conceal a material fact; or
Otherwise commit a fraud in making the application.
